Package gw.plugin.addressbook

Interface IAddressBookAdapter

All Superinterfaces:
InternalPlugin, Remote
@Deprecated public interface IAddressBookAdapter extends InternalPlugin
Deprecated.
Guidewire application interface to an Address Book. This plugin has been deprecated.

  • Method Details

    • retrieveContact

      Contact retrieveContact(String addressBookUId, ContactRelationshipSpec contactRelationshipSpec) throws RemoteException
      Deprecated.
      Since ClaimCenter 8.0 Use retrieveContact() in ContactSystemPlugin
      Looks up the contact with the given Address Book ID. Specifies relationships to include with the given ContactRelationshipSpec.
      Throws:
      RemoteException

    • retrieveRelatedContacts

      Contact retrieveRelatedContacts(Contact contact, ContactRelationshipSpec contactRelationshipSpec) throws RemoteException
      Deprecated.
      Since ClaimCenter 8.0 Use retrieveRelatedContacts() in ContactSystemPlugin
      Retrieves related contacts for a given Contact, for example if the Contact had originally been retrieved with a restrictive ContactRelationshipSpec. Specifies relationships to include with the given ContactRelationshipSpec.
      Parameters:
      contact - a contact retrieved from an addressbook search. This contact will populated with all related contacts retrieved from the addressbook.
      Returns:
      the modified contact. This must be the same as the Contact provided.
      Throws:
      RemoteException

    • findDefinitiveMatch

      ContactFindMatchResult findDefinitiveMatch(Contact contactData) throws RemoteException
      Deprecated.
      Since ClaimCenter 8.0 Use findDuplicates() in ContactSystemPlugin.
      Searches for a contact that definitively matches the given contact data.
      Throws:
      RemoteException

    • findPotentialMatches

      ContactSearchResult findPotentialMatches(Contact contactData, AddressBookRemotableSearchResultSpec searchResultSpec) throws RemoteException
      Deprecated.
      Since ClaimCenter 8.0 Use findDuplicates() in ContactSystemPlugin
      Searches for all contacts that potentially match the given contact data. Results are specified by the given SearchResultSpec.
      Throws:
      RemoteException

    • searchContact

      ContactSearchResult searchContact(ContactSearchCriteria searchCriteria, AddressBookRemotableSearchResultSpec searchResultSpec) throws RemoteException
      Deprecated.
      Since ClaimCenter 8.0 Use searchContacts() in ContactSystemPlugin
      Searches for all contacts that match the given search criteria. Results are specified by the given SearchResultSpec.
      Throws:
      RemoteException

    • submitUpdates

      ContactUpdateResult submitUpdates(UpdateBatch updates, Contact contact) throws RemoteException
      Deprecated.
      Since ClaimCenter 8.0 Use updateContact() in ContactSystemPlugin
      Updates (or creates if not already exists) AddressBook Contacts as specified in the UpdateBatch parameter.
      Parameters:
      updates - the set of update operations to be performed in the address book
      contact - the Contact being updated or created
      Throws:
      RemoteException
